  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ActivityPort
    A Port that specifies the data consumed or produced by an Activity.
    DepthPort  
    GranularDepthPort  
    InputPort
    A Port that specifies inputs to a Workflow component.
    OutputPort
    A Port that specifies outputs from a Workflow component.
    Port
    A Port specifies the data consumed or produced by a Workflow component.
    ProcessorPort
    A Port that specifies the data consumed or produced by an Processor.
    ReceiverPort
    A Port that receives data from a DataLink in a Workflow.
    SenderPort
    A Port that sends data out to a DataLink in a Workflow.
    WorkflowPort
